-- Cerberus interested in BlackBerry - Dow Jones
-- 
-- Wed Oct 2, 2013 2:53pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/02/us-blackberry-offer-idUSBRE9910Y220131002

 

 TORONTO  (Reuters) - BlackBerry Ltd has drawn interest from private equity group Cerberus and at least one other investor, CNBC said on Wednesday, quoting Dow Jones, which cited unnamed sources. 
 Shares of BlackBerry jumped as the news hit, and were up 2.5 percent at $8.11 on Nasdaq. (Reporting by  Alastair Sharp ; Editing by Gerald E. McCormick)